   visualize the on-going advancements of early scientific research on
   COVID-19 from the perspective of AI. By adopting the Latent Dirichlet
   Allocation (LDA) model, this paper allocates the research articles into
   50 key research topics pertinent to COVID-19 according to their
   abstracts. We present an overview of early studies of the COVID-19
