Abstract = {Purpose This paper throws light on some of the nature of artificial
   intelligence (AI) development, which will serve as a starter for helping
   to advance its development. Design/methodology/approach This work
   reveals the evolutions and trends of AI from four dimensions: research,
   output, influence and competition through leveraging academic knowledge
   graph with 130,750 AI scholars and 43,746 scholarly articles. Findings
